# Jameson Walter PA1
# To run the program, have the Makefile and main.cc in a directory.
# Type the following commands into the terminal:
# make
# ./main (followed by 5 aguements listed below)
# arg1 - B (Block Cipher) or S (Stream Cipher)
# arg2 - input file containing the plaintext or ciphertext
# arg3 - output file
# arg4 - input file containing the key
# arg5 - E (Encrypt) or D (Decrypt)